leaves, then strain out as per the recipe.","If the granita becomes too firm to serve, place into the refrigerator or leave on the kitchen bench until thawed to your desired softness before serving. Scrape across the surface with a fork or spoon to serve. You may wish to store all frozen desserts in individual portions, as refreezing thawed leftovers can be a safety hazard."],"basicInfo":["medium","15m","40m","4 portions"]}